(44, 8, 13, 42, 8, 13, 13, 'believed also', 'Belief and Temptation Connection', 'This connection highlights the theme of belief in both passages. In Acts, Simon believes and is baptized, while in Luke, those who receive the word with joy may fall away in times of temptation.', 'theme', 0.314, 'medium', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
